cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO 

This paper deals with computer vision and natural language processing, specifically in the task of change captioning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). However, since the paper also involves language modeling and attention mechanisms, it could also belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper uses machine learning techniques to perform the task, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, since the paper deals with localization of changes, it could also be relevant to cs.RO (Robotics).
